{"tid":1324923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逆權運動】黎智英晤對華鷹派亞太助理國務卿 討論香港情況","createTime":"2019-07-16T16:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T04:06:30.000Z","uid":227801,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"374d406474528c7f6f63674595adbfb9cd0d8085","tid":1324923,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:55:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190717/59831470\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190717%2F59831470&d=4wcocBccBPvk8MIeFEbr%2BUB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=b2efda5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190717%2F59831470&h=ad321317\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190717/59831470</a><br />\n黎智英與史迪威會面，討論香港情況。<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒集團創辦人黎智英近日與主張對華強硬、主管亞太事務的美國助理國務卿史迪威（David Stilwell）會面，討論香港情況。<br />\n<br />\n黎智英在近期美國之行，已先後獲美國副總統彭斯、國務卿蓬佩奧、國家安全顧問博爾頓，以及多位參議員接見，並接受霍士新聞頻道節目訪問。黎智英曾表示希望美國支持港人，以彰顯其道德權威。<br />\n<br />\n史迪威是退役空軍准將，1980年加入美國空軍，會說中文和韓語，被視為「亞洲通」，2011年至2013年任職美國駐華大使館武官，也曾在更名為印太司令部的太平洋司令部任職，2015年退役。有專家與前任官員認為，史迪威對中國競爭具有深入戰略思想，對盟友角色與台灣獨特地位也有深切概念。太平洋司令部司令前顧問塞耶茲（Eric Sayers）曾表示，史迪威是不錯的選擇，北京不會喜歡，意味特朗普的選擇正確。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普去年10月提名史迪威出任主管亞太事務的助理國務卿，提名上月獲參議院確認。<br />\n史迪威上周展開上任後首次亞洲之旅，訪問日本、南韓，菲律賓、泰國等盟友，討論地區經濟及安全問題。"},{"pid":"5645fe8378104007f4aaf4794dc7e82d83a6ab62","tid":1324923,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8578244b628d44b60bb7533fcd545632d1ccabf0","tid":1324923,"uid":266309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:59:31.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a1ab1e669d33322278c4f9e3d64b2be9af3b96","tid":1324923,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:03:18.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"8111b731b6dd6cd498378ec12d5090c403508bb7","tid":1324923,"uid":41458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:05:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大家保持清醒, 林鄭只係一個傀儡<br />\n送中呢條法例牽涉兩地司法制度, 佢冇可能夠膽自己推<br />\n絕對係中央同西環, 為左配合大灣區發展而落既指示<br />\n不過今次香港市民反應極大就推林鄭出嚟揹左佢<br />\n成個政府畀中央同西環操控晒, 一國兩制名存實亡, 已經係公開既秘密<br />\n林鄭下唔下台作用不大, 中央只會任命聽話既人<br />\n一定要將唯命是從嘅警察高層, 同政府大片染紅高官徹底剷除<br />\n實行全面普選<br />\n香港先會有一線生機</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求, 不徹不散"},{"pid":"7e0d1e40741252002555768c5bb49398858082ab","tid":1324923,"uid":149361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9873b386370c6f6e3e3987fdf9ae8d79635b46a","tid":1324923,"uid":54125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:08:19.000Z","msg":"係咪成個美國政界都畀肥佬黎見晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04bad024316dddd40398f2d8926ca6c47b864dc6","tid":1324923,"uid":266874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:08:27.000Z","msg":"肥佬黎好堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5837b1dd0d8a77e1d443235887fd9337dbdd4fd4","tid":1324923,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9873b386370c6f6e3e3987fdf9ae8d79635b46a","tid":1324923,"uid":54125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:08:19.000Z","msg":"係咪成個美國政界都畀肥佬黎見晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:10:02.000Z","msg":"除咗trump"},{"pid":"527417127a94aba98fd197aaf80af17c6f7aeb6c","tid":1324923,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:1